k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Rafaella,<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please see below <s=
pan style=3D"color:#0070C0">
[in blue] </span>my responses to the questions in your email below dated Se=
ptember 6, 2025.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please also find at=
tached a copy of the =E2=80=98Material Damage Report=E2=80=99 &amp; the =E2=
=80=98Scope of Works=E2=80=99 which relates to the damage report.<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have done my best=
 to answer the specific questions that you have raised. My general response=
 to your enquiries is summarised as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo10"><span sty=
le=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All material and documentation of any form, in resp=
ect of your claim, is discoverable and is available to be provided to you. =
This will remain your enduring right through-out
 the claim process.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" st=
yle=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo10"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I will ne=
ed to work closely with your Claim Manager to ensure the information that y=
ou are requesting is provided to you in a timely manner. I am wiling to ass=
ist the
 Claims Manager in this respect.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoList=
Paragraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo10"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0=
pt">All aspects of potential damage which you are seeking to receive assura=
nces on can be responded to on an individual basis. I am unable to provide =
those responses to
 you in this email, as I will require consultation and input from the relev=
ant specialists and consultants.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I think the most co=
nstructive next step would be for me to schedule a meeting with the key sta=
keholders within Tower Insurance and following that provide you with the cl=
arification that you have requested.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please allow me to =
schedule a meeting with my colleagues and take the time required to provide=
 you with a considered and comprehensive response.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. <o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
